-- Baird Says Canada Will Suspend Diplomatic Operations At Embassy in Syria
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2012-03-05T18:46:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-05/baird-says-canada-will-suspend-diplomatic-operations-at-embassy-in-syria.html
Canada is suspending work at its
embassy in Damascus, Foreign Affairs Minister  John Baird  said.  “Canada is suspending its operations in our mission in
Damascus” Baird said at a press conference in Ottawa, saying
the move is effective immediately. He also reiterated that
 Syria ’s President Bashar al-Assad should resign because of
attacks on his own people.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Greg Quinn in Ottawa at 
